definitions.definition: The process of ingesting , or consuming something orally , whether it be food, drink, medicine, or other substance. It is usually referred to as the first step of digestion.
The process of ingesting something into a jet engine or an instance.
Any intake of a substance into an organism.
Intake of data into a computer system.
